{
  "stem": "8947.1",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And at that time, the girls were up and the women, and the men were down.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And he was a very handsome man, you know.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And many girls had a crush on him, too.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "But then naturally, we had a Friday night dinner.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And my mother made the best fish.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And [SOBBING] I wish she would be alive.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "Forgive me, but I lost her last year.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And when you talk about this, I remember the times, you know, when I can see her lighting the candles and-- and-- and the beautiful things on the table and the nice cakes that she made.",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "My mother was a great cook.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "And that was-- that was the Shabbat, you know And on the-- on the Shabbat, we got together with the family.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "We were a large family, you see.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "I have cousins, many cousins.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "And my mother had sisters.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "And-- and Saturday was a time when, you know, after lunch a family got together.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "Or, we had lunch together.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "My grandparents had a big house at that time.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "My grandfather was a businessman.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "And then sometimes we will go all there, you know.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "And it was-- it was specials.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "Our holidays were-- were celebrated in a very special way.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "And I remember-- I remember the Passover.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "Now, you're not good to see Passover celebrated like in our home.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "Maybe you do.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "But my father put on his white robe.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "And he put the pillows, bright pillows of the chair.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "And then we had the Haggadah, everyone following all the ritual.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 42,
      "text": "And naturally, the [NON-ENGLISH], it's called, you know, the matzoh is put for me to find.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 43,
      "text": "And-- and-- and I wanted to look where he put it.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 44,
      "text": "And-- and I a little bit opening my eyes.",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
